snippet.description:
Adley and Niko have the BEST NIGHT EVER at our new favorite place!!

JOIN OUR FAM!! --- http://goo.gl/rfgp8V

Best Ball Pit Day Ever 1015

We were not ready for this!! I got home from the spacestation and Jenny said she found this new place not far from us that was a brand new indoor park. Adley is a little daredevil, she has no fear! They have an obstacle course machine on some trampolines and Adley does amazing at it!!

They also have a sky coaster track that Jenny and I took turns riding on. Adley was just a little to short to ride, but she had fun watching her mom and dad zip around the ceiling. We had so much fun and as we were getting ready to leave, we found even more things for us to do. We're definitely going to come back! 

Everyone really needs to check this place out. This isn't a brand deal or a partnership, me and my family genuinely had so much fun that I wanted to give them a shout out and thank them for the amazing time!!

snippet.title: Fun Indoor Playground for Kids and Family at Kids Kingdom
snippet.description: This is the Kids Kingdom indoor playground at Bilzen, Belgium. It is called KinderRijck in Dutch. It is one of the largest indoor playground in Belgium. The playground has a very large soft play area, inflatables, a mini drop tower, a wave swinger and even a rope parcours for kids and their parents. We paid 10 € per kid, parents don’t have to pay!
